Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to Police Officer Frederick G. Maley
Summary: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to Police Officer Frederick G. Maley in the hamlet of North Bellmore, town of Hempstead, county of Nassau.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to Police Officer Frederick G. Maley
